# My Thyme website created using MERN stack

## Project Goals

The purpose of this project is to create a website that allows a user to upload cooking recipe blog posts and have other users read and comment on those posts.

## Requirements

### Login

    Users will be able to log in to their accounts to identify their comments and restrict blog posting ability to the main user.

### Create Recipes

    The main user will be able to store recipes to the database that can be reused across blogs.
    Recipes will include:
    - Name
    - Ingredients
    - Instructions
    - Cook time
    - Prep time

### Create blog posts

    The main user will be able to create and edit blogs with the following features.
    - Write and format text for the post
    - Embed photos within the post
    - Embed recipes within the post

### Write comments

    Other users will be able to post comments below blog posts and respond to each other's comments.

### Moderate comments

    The main user will be able to delete or block comments of the other users
